      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This powerplant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a split-sump oiling system to maintain lubrication during high lateral G-loads. The engine delivers a linear power curve up to an 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque vectoring. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), offering adjustable compression and rebound cycles to suit varying road surfaces. Recent service includes preventative rod bearing replacement and updated throttle valve actuators, ensuring the longevity of the rotating assembly. The subframe mounting points and suspension bushings remain tight, preserving the precision of the factory steering geometry and kinematic response.",
